snippet.title: CatchKing Trailer for Eden Games
snippet.description:
Help Catch complete his quest to collect absolutely everything, in this nostalgic inspired Rouge-lite collectathon built on the solana blockchain. Defeat powerful bosses, explore dungeons, collect rare fish, manage resources, duel pets and hangout with other players! CatchKing is an exciting, fresh, indie game first, and a blockchain game second, bringing the power of the marketplace and item ownership to the hands of players.

Check out these links below to learn more!
Twitter: https://twitter.com/catch_king
Magic Eden: https://www.magiceden.io/games/catchking
Website: https://www.catchking.io/

Buy your CatchKing Explorer Here: https://magiceden.io/marketplace/catchking_explorers
